¶

If a footnote is referenced multiple times[NTE:times], it will be displayed
multiple times with the same content but different numbering.[NTE:one]

This is some text with a short footnote\NTE[The use of footnotes should be discouraged!] in the middle of it.\NTE[Really!]

*	NTE:times
	Any number of times.

